Enable lexical-binding
Add CI and FUNDING.yml

Consistently adjust the zero-based error columns from package-lint

Flycheck considers the first column to be 1, while Emacs uses
0. `package-lint` now consistently produces zero-based columns in
error positions.

Prefer "elisp" for code blocks

Thanks @Alhadis
Add Patreon badge

Give a hint about what "metadata" means

Closes #4, thanks @DamienCassou

Merge pull request #2 from Fanael/master

Downgrade non-standard keyword diagnostic to warning

Fixes #37.
